install requires the following environment variables to be set: 

XERCESCROOT       the path to the xerces install e.g. XERCESCROOT=/sandbox/xerces-c-src_2_3_0
BOOSTROOT         the path to the boost install e.g.  BOOSTROOT=/sandbox/boost_1_29_0
XAIFBOOSTERROOT   the path to the xaifBooster install, i.e. the parent of the xaifBooster directory, 
		  e.g. XAIFBOOSTERROOT=/sandbox/xaifBooster_current

and for the test driver that uses the ANGEL library: 
ANGELROOT         the path to the ANGEL install, e.g. ANGELROOT=/sandbox/CVS/angel
                  Note, in order to build ANGEL for use with xaifBooster edit 
		  $(ANGELROOT)/specs/lib_usage.conf and make sure
			CPPFLAGS	+= -DUSE_XAIF
		  and 
			CPPFLAGS	+= -I$(XAIF_DIR)
		  are not commented out and XAIF_DIR (used by the angel build) 
		  is set to the same value as XAIFBOOSTERROOT

before any make do: 

	cd ${XAIFBOOSTERROOT}/xaifBooster

to make all object files and libraries: 
	make 

to make all test drivers: 
	make test

to create doxygen html files: 
	make doc


